These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, polish
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: lacrosse, baseball
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, bike
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
2. the polish is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | polish    | argentine |
| Sport         | baseball | lacrosse    |
| Transport     | ship     | bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, australian
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the dutch is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | milk  | almond-milk   |
| Nationality   | australian | dutch  |
| Transport     | helicopter   | car |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, fishing
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, spy
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, climbing
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an even position##4
2. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Hobby         | filmmaking   | fishing  |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | action  |
| Sport         | rugby   | climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
There 2 different types of food: apricot, radish
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: spy, disaster
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, subway
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
2. the person eating apricot is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Food          | apricot | radish |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster   | spy   |
| Transport     | subway       | motorbike      |

