.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: rock-climbing, skydiving
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, hip-hop
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: parkour, sailing
1. the fan of classical is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing    | skydiving    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop     | classical      |
| Sport         | parkour | sailing |

