.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There 2 different types of food: kale, blueberry
The people have 2 different jobs:  chef, bartender
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, cricket
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the chef##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
3. the person eating kale is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | blueberry | kale     |
| Job     | bartender | chef |
| Sport   | cricket | handball    |

 #################################

 
