.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-14::.
There 2 different types of food: pear, peach
The people have 2 different hobbies: reading, filmmaking
2 different pets are kept: hamster, ferret
1. the owner of the ferret is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |
| Food    | peach | pear  |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | reading |
| Pet     | hamster  | ferret     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, chess
There are 2 different nationalities: american, spanish
2 different pets are kept: fish, hamster
1. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
2. the american is on the left of the spanish##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Hobby         | chess | puzzles |
| Nationality   | american     | spanish     |
| Pet           | hamster          | fish     |

 #################################

 
